    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Hostels: Newly constructed hostels with all things that we need. We have washing machine to clean clothes, we have 24*7 lights, sry guys no AC is here in hostel rooms. But we have 9-10 study rooms where you can study, watch movie also.",
          "name": "Ashish Ranjan",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Academic: Every year the curriculum is getting more better. Everything here is outstanding. Major Minor rule is here. The course is also easy to moderate level. Each semester is of 4 months with 2 quizzes, mid semester and end semester exams",
          "name": "Prapulla M",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "As permanent campus is far from city, you may feel that there's nothing to enjoy but wait, Tirupati is a city not developed like Pune but it's good for us. Even we go for trekking also. There's lots of places. Bangalore and pondi, is also not far.",
          "name": "Ashish Ranjan",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Provides good exposure. There are a lot of seminars held",
          "name": "Lokesh Kumar Panagar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The time boundaries is one of the thing I don't like. As we all are college students and we are not child anymore but after all this there are restrictions on us. You can't outside of the campus after 6 PM. We have to return to room before 12:30AM",
          "name": "Ashish Ranjan",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "Connectivity: The college is far from city approx 31km, but local buses and auto are available.",
          "name": "Prapulla M",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is mandatory 80 percent attendance and i personaly do not like it",
          "name": "Lokesh Kumar Panagar",
          "course_tag_name": "BS + MS"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
